{
  "stem": "2590.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then we came back to the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And right away, there were orders that all Jews should give all the gold, silver, chrome, copper, bicycles, and radios to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father worked with this Russian engineer whose name was Gavrilov, and they were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even my mother and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gavrilov were friendly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They also had two children approximately my age or my sister's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Gavrilov told my father, why should you supply your blood enemy with all the goodies?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Give them just a token of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the rest, you can come to me, and we'll build a bunker, and we'll put away everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in case an emergency will come, you'll come to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, my father and Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gavrilov, they lived in the outskirts of Rowne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a nice house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took out from the veranda a few boards, and supported it with pillars, and put in blankets, and benches, and put some dry food-- dry bread.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We should be able to live in case of an emergency.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we remembered it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought if the time will come, we'll use it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the meantime, there were also [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] notes all over the city that all the-- all the intelligentsia and all professional people should meet.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember, it was a temple or was it a school?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they want to get ideas how to make a ghetto or where to make the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, my father went also, and he never came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans figured that as soon they'll get rid of the intellectuals of the intelligentsia, the masses-- they'll be able to do with the masses whatever that would be convenient for them.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
